      "category": "ai",
      "title": "Self-Hosted AI news aggregator using Cloudflare Workers, Vectorize, and Nostr",
      "url": "https://github.com/delirehberi/news",
      "discuss_url": "https://lobste.rs/s/u7ls6b",
      "score": 1,
      "comments": 0,
      "author": "delirehberi",
      "published": "2026-07-03T15:26:27Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Uses @cf/baai/bge-base-en-v1.5 natively within Cloudflare Workers AI for 768-dimension embeddings with zero external cold starts.",
        "Runs Cosine Similarity calculations on Cloudflare Vectorize against bootstrapped user preference profiles ingested from RSS or JSON.",
        "Built on Cloudflare's edge stack using Hono on Workers, D1 for relational storage, and background cron jobs for JSON polling."
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "lobsters",
      "subsource": "lobste.rs/programming",
      "category": "engineering",
      "title": "Gossamer",
      "url": "https://gossamer-lang.org/",
